  "body": "Docker, Windows & macos\r\n\r\n\r\n`docker run -it -v e:/prysm:/data --network=\"host\" gcr.io/prysmaticlabs/prysm/validator:latest --keystore-path=/data --datadir=/data --password=yourPassword --medalla`\r\n\r\n`docker run -it -v e:/prysm/:/data -p 4000:4000 -p 13000:13000 gcr.io/prysmaticlabs/prysm/beacon-chain:latest --datadir=/data --medalla`\r\n\r\n![cmd_2020-07-27_13-19-54](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26490734/88536300-e72e2480-d00b-11ea-8daf-6536bd4c8689.png)\r\n\r\n**Error during sync** \r\n`FATAL validator: Could not determine if beacon chain started: could not setup beacon chain ChainStart streaming client: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = write tcp 127.0.0.1:53340->127.0.0.1:4000: write: broken pipe`\r\n\r\n**Error once synced** \r\n`FATAL validator: Could not determine if beacon chain started: could not setup beacon chain ChainStart streaming client: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection closed`\r\n",
